{
  "texts": [
    "These approaches help stakeholders understand and trust the decisions made by AI systems, facilitating their integration into critical applications (Muñoz and Iglesias, 2024).",
    "Scalability is another challenge that affects the deployment of NLP systems.",
    "Scaling these systems across various platforms and environments requires careful management of computational resources, which can be complex due to the diverse and distributed nature of modern infrastructures.",
    "In real-time applications, this challenge is amplified by the need for consistent performance (Khaleel et al., 2024).",
    "Solution: Utilizing a hybrid cloud-edge architecture can improve scalability by distributing processing loads between cloud servers and edge devices."
  ]
}